---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import authorImage from "../assets/tk-author-image.png";
---

<Layout title="About Topher Knowles | The Veilhost Trilogy">
	<section class="about page-shell">
		<div class="headshot">
			<img src={authorImage.src} alt="Topher Knowles" />
		</div>
		<div class="about-copy">
			<p class="kicker">About the author</p>
			<h1>Topher Knowles</h1>
			<p>
				Topher Knowles is the author of The Veilhost Trilogy, his debut fantasy series
				and a world he has been shaping for the past ten years. His love of fantasy
				began when a friend lent him a copy of Raymond E. Feist's Magician, opening
				the door to the kind of sweeping stories, strange magic, and unforgettable
				characters that have inspired him ever since.
			</p>
			<p>
				Originally drawn to stories with mystery, danger, and a sense of worlds larger
				than their maps, Topher now lives in Manchester, England, where he has made
				his home for twenty years. He shares it with his wife, Ruth, and their dopey
				Golden Retriever, Buddy.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.about {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: minmax(220px, 0.38fr) minmax(0, 0.62fr);
		gap: clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
		align-items: center;
		padding: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem) 0;
	}

	.headshot {
		aspect-ratio: 4 / 4;
		background:
			linear-gradient(rgba(8, 7, 5, 0.16), rgba(8, 7, 5, 0.16)),
			var(--color-white);
		border: 3px solid var(--color-black);
		box-shadow: 12px 12px 0 var(--color-black);
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.headshot img {
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		object-fit: cover;
	}

	.about-copy {
		background: var(--color-white);
		padding: clamp(1.4rem, 4vw, 3rem);
	}

	.kicker {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		font-size: 0.78rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		letter-spacing: 0.12em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}

	h1 {
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-size: clamp(4rem, 12vw, 8rem);
	}

	p:last-child {
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	@media (max-width: 760px) {
		.about {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
